---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { getSiteConfig, getPersona } from '../lib/config'
const cfg = getSiteConfig()
const persona = getPersona()
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`How We Test — ${cfg.site.brand_name}`}
  description={`Our testing methodology: how ${persona.name_used} evaluates garden tools, furniture, and equipment before recommending them.`}
>
  <div class="container" style="padding-top:2rem; padding-bottom:4rem; max-width:720px;">
    <h1>How We Test</h1>
    <p>Every product on this site has been tested in a real garden in Litchfield County, Connecticut, through real seasons. That means full summers for tools, full winters for furniture, and more than one growing season before a verdict.</p>
    <h2>What we actually do</h2>
    <p>We buy or borrow the products we test. We use them. We note what breaks, what wears, and what still looks good after a year. We revisit our picks when newer versions come out and update when our opinion changes.</p>
    <h2>What we don't do</h2>
    <p>We don't accept free products in exchange for positive reviews. We don't write "best of" lists based on Amazon ratings. We don't recommend products we haven't used or wouldn't buy with our own money.</p>
    <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you buy something through one, we earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This never influences what we recommend — see our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">full affiliate disclosure</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
